✨ Full Stack Realtime Chat App ✨



🔥 Highlights
🌟 Tech stack: MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js) + Socket.io + TailwindCSS + Daisy UI
🎃 Authentication & Authorization: Secure login using JWT (JSON Web Token)
👾 Real-time messaging: Powered by Socket.io for seamless live chats
🚀 Online user status: Display real-time online users
👌 Global state management: Handled using Zustand
🐞 Robust error handling: Implemented on both server and client sides
⭐ Deployment: Step-by-step guide for FREE deployment!
⏳ More Features: Additional capabilities to explore and enhance
🛠️ Environment Setup
To run the application locally, create a .env file in the root directory and add the following environment variables:

env
Copy code
MONGODB_URI=your-mongodb-uri
PORT=5001
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret

CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your-cloudinary-cloud-name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your-cloudinary-api-key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your-cloudinary-api-secret

NODE_ENV=development
🚀 Build and Run the App
Build
bash
Copy code
npm run build
Start
bash
Copy code
npm start

🌐 Deployment
Follow the detailed deployment guide included in the documentation to host your app FOR FREE on platforms like Vercel, Netlify, or Heroku.

Feel free to explore the app, contribute, or provide feedback. Happy coding! 🎉

